# Custom TextFSM Template Index
#
# This file registers custom templates for auto-discovery.
# Format: Template, Hostname, Platform, Command
#
# - Template: Filename of template (in this directory)
# - Hostname: Regex to match device hostname (use .* for all)
# - Platform: Device platform (e.g., cisco_ios, arista_eos)
# - Command: Regex to match command
#
# Templates in this index are checked BEFORE ntc-templates (929 built-in templates).
# If no match is found here, ntc-templates will be used automatically.
#
# Example entries (uncomment to use):
# custom_show_version.textfsm, .*, cisco_ios, show version
# datacenter_bgp.textfsm, dc-.*, cisco_ios, show ip bgp.*
# special_interfaces.textfsm, router-[0-9]+, cisco_ios, show ip int.*

Template, Hostname, Platform, Command
custom_show_version.textfsm, .*, cisco_ios, show version
my_parser.textfsm, .*, cisco_ios, show ip int brief
